187
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:02,680
Sure.

188
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,150
Okay.

189
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:03,780
Why do you girls

190
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:05,520
