191
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:06,870
Come on.

192
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:09,310
This kind of town is actually very special.

193
00:15:09,310 --> 00:15:10,510
It's worth visiting.

194
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,440
What do you know?

195
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,150
