203
00:15:43,190 --> 00:15:44,680
I suddenly remembered

204
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:48,030
Nan Hua said he was going fishing this morning.

205
00:15:48,310 --> 00:15:49,110
He went fishing.

206
00:15:49,110 --> 00:15:50,720
