246
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,720
I meant yesterday.

247
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,150
Yesterday?

248
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:02,840
It was great yesterday.

249
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:03,990
Well...

250
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,210
