265
00:18:51,870 --> 00:18:52,560
Really?

266
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,680
Yes.

267
00:18:54,830 --> 00:18:57,030
I like you very, very, very much!

268
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,430
Leave the rest

269
00:19:02,430 --> 00:19:04,360
